188
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:25,150
I wanted to approach Xiao Li

189
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:26,910
to ferret out the accomplice.

190
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,360
But it turns out

191
00:13:30,510 --> 00:13:32,480
that person is well-hidden,

192
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,910
far more slippery than Xiao Li.

193
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:37,720
