to find any trace of him.

194
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:42,840
♪As the heavy rain pours down♪

195
00:13:42,870 --> 00:13:44,000
At first,

196
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:46,390
I planned take revenge on Xiao Shizhao

197
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:49,120
because he was the culprit.

198
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,960
But he died before I took action.

199
00:13:53,770 --> 00:13:55,550
♪If not for that fateful mistake♪

200
00:13:55,550 --> 00:13:56,670
So Xiao Li was my next target.

